<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3785858>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–11. Telostholus bifasciatus sp. nov., ♂, holotype. 1 and 2, habitus (1, in lateral view; 2, in dorsal view). 3, head in frontal view. 4, head in lateral view. 5, head and pronotum in dorsal view. 6, mesosoma part. in dorsal view. 7, fore wing. 8, hind wing. 9, genitalia in ventral view. 10, hypopygium in ventral view. 11, S6 in ventral view. Scale bar: 1.0 mm for 1, 2; 0.5 mm for 6–8; 0.2 mm for 3–5, 9–11." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3785858/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3785864>
    dc:description "FIGURES 34–44. Telostholus tomentosus sp. nov., ♀, holotype. 34, clypeus and labrum in frontal view. 35 and 36, habitus (35, in lateral view; 36, in dorsal view). 37, head in frontal view. 38, head in lateral view. 39, head, pronotum, and mesoscutum in dorsal view. 40, mesosoma part. in dorsal view. 41, propodeum in dorso-lateral view. 42, propodeum in lateral view. 43, fore wing. 44, hind wing. Scale bar: 1.0 mm for 35, 36, 43, 44; 0.5 mm for 39, 40; 0.2 mm for 34, 37, 38, 41, 42." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3785864/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

